An opinion is attached with emotions and in more wits its interpretation of facts. “Opinions” are key influencers of someone’s behavior. For a product, it’s a thinking that leads to a decision, where a product stands. Through opinion mining, we can know about contents of whole product opinions. Opinion mining (sentiment analysis) is a challenge where opinions mean less efforts and best results to correct information about a product. Opinions are not a dissertation which can be left unread but it’s a track to reach in mind of people to get views about a product. This paper presents an algorithm to extract opinions from a micro blogging site on which an organization trusts and consider its reviews. By this technique, database of online opinions can be created by far.